<plot>A day in the life of Shane - the lead singer of the L.A. rock band Dirty Virgin. Shane has her pick of admirers but it's her roommate Dustin she wants to be with. As Shane works the courage to share her feeling with Dustin, he meets Cali and Shane's shot at love starts to dwindle. With Dirty Virgin about to embark on a world tour, will Dustin realize that he's the object of Shane's affections? Will they risk their friendship to give this Love Song a chance?</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?344931</url></doc>
